            512
        ],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The molecular weight of oxygen is 0.032 kg/mol and of nitrogen is 0.028 kg/mol. Condition: 25 oC and 101300 Pa abs. ",
